    62→@dataclass
    63→class TypeCheckConfiguration:
    64→    """
    65→     You can change Typeguard's behavior with these settings.
    66→
    67→    .. attribute:: typecheck_fail_callback
    68→       :type: Callable[[TypeCheckError, TypeCheckMemo], Any]
    69→
    70→         Callable that is called when type checking fails.
    71→
